name: Kanaria Genesis Back
description: Minted as part of the [Kanaria](https://kanaria.rmrk.app) genesis set of items, these NFTs can be equipped into the "back" slot on Kanaria birds.

name: Kanaria Genesis Front
description: Minted as part of the [Kanaria](https://kanaria.rmrk.app) genesis set of items, these NFTs can be equipped into the "front" slot on Kanaria birds. This can be anything that isn't a pendant/necklace, like a vest, a tie, or even props like surfboards and other foreground items that are in front of the bird.

name: Kanaria Genesis Location
description: [Kanaria](https://kanaria.rmrk.app) background locations. These are backdrops that place the Kanaria birds in various rooms and locations around the Kanaria universe, and further decorate your cards. These locations may have additional functionality later on, so collecting a diverse set could be useful.

name: Kanaria Genesis Chest
description: [Kanaria](https://kanaria.rmrk.app) chest equippables. These are NFTs that visually improve the Kanaria bird's chest region - medals, pendants, shirts. They might bestow additional features on their wearer in the future, so collecting a wide set of diverse items may be beneficial.

name: Kanaria Genesis Headwear
description: [Kanaria](https://kanaria.rmrk.app) headwear. These are NFTs that visually improve the Kanaria bird's head region - hats, caps, hairdo, even goggles and glasses. They might bestow additional features on their wearer in the future, so collecting a wide set of diverse items may be beneficial.

name: Kanaria Genesis Handheld
description: Kanaria Handheld items. These standalone NFTs have additional resources allowing you to equip them into Kanaria genesis birds originally, and other projects later. They go into the left or right hand / wing.
